</div></div><div id="recentposts-2" class="module nocontent widget_recentposts"><h4 class="moduleHeader">Recent Posts</h4>				<div class="entry">
						<h5><a href="//economix.blogs.nytimes.com/2014/04/22/economix-meets-the-gales-of-change/" title="Read: Economix Meets the Gales of Change">Economix Meets the Gales of Change</a>
			<span class="postMetaHeaderCommentCount commentCount hidden">
					<i class="icon"></i>
					<a class="commentCountLink commentCountNumberOnly commentCountNoPrompt" href="//economix.blogs.nytimes.com/2014/04/22/economix-meets-the-gales-of-change/"></a>
				</span>			</h5>
			<p class="summary">
			Economix is coming to an end, but it will be succeeded by The Upshot, a new politics, policy and economics site. <a href="//economix.blogs.nytimes.com/2014/04/22/economix-meets-the-gales-of-change/" class="more-link">Read&#160;more&#8230;</a></p>
